DataList.LocalizeJP: 美味しいから分けてあげるよ～
DataList.LocalizeEN: I'll share it since it's so delicious~.

DataList.LocalizeJP:
うぅ、めんどくさい……
……よし、これなら！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Hmph such a pain... Alright maybe this will work...

DataList.LocalizeJP:
休みた～い……
あ、そうだ！
DataList.LocalizeEN: I wanna rest. Ah, I know!

DataList.LocalizeJP:
何かいい方法は……
……よし！これで完了！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Is there any good way to.... Okay, this does it!

DataList.LocalizeJP: 終わったら、ドーナッツでも食べよっかな～
DataList.LocalizeEN: Once we're finished, let's eat some donuts~.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 当たっても知らないからね～
DataList.LocalizeEN: Not my problem if it hit you, got it~

DataList.LocalizeJP: まぁ、別にこれでいいよね～

えぇ……あんま頑張りたくないんだけど……
まぁ、一応ありがたく貰うね。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Ehh.. I don't really wanna work that hard though... Well, I'm grateful regardless

DataList.LocalizeJP:
え？ほんとにいいの？
私、そこまでやる気ないんだけど……
DataList.LocalizeEN: Eh? Are you sure? I'm really not that motivated though...

DataList.LocalizeJP:
その……ここまでしてくれなくても、
先生がプールに入る時くらい、ちゃんと見守ってあげるからさ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Um... You don't have to do all this for me, if it's just looking out for you at the pool I'll do that no problems

DataList.LocalizeJP:
気は進まないけど……もらった分は仕事しなきゃだよねぇ……
できれば、ドーナッツもくれたら嬉しいんだけど……
DataList.LocalizeEN:
I don't really wanna do it but... I guess I'll have to return the favor at least...
I'd be happy if I'd get some donuts though...

DataList.LocalizeJP:
サボってないよ～ちゃんと仕事中。
目は動かしてるからさ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: I'm not slacking off~ I'm really doing work. My eyes are moving after all.

DataList.LocalizeJP:
先生もプール気持ちいい？
ほら、隣に座って一休みしよ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Does the pool feel good Sensei? Here, sit by me and let's take a break.

DataList.LocalizeJP:
どうせサボるなら……
先生と一緒にサボっていたいよね、ふふ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: If I'm going to slack of... I'd love to slack off with you, hehe

DataList.LocalizeJP: ちょうどいいサイズの浮き輪。流れるプール……う～ん極楽……先生も一緒にどう？
DataList.LocalizeEN: A nicely sized floaty, flowing water in the pool... Mhmm this is paradise. How about we enjoy it together, sensei?
